net.minecraftforge.client

Interface SkyRenderHandler

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IRenderHandler

    public interface SkyRenderHandler
extends IRenderHandler
    Call Dimension.setSkyRenderer(net.minecraftforge.client.IRenderHandler) with an implementation of this to override all sky rendering with your own. This includes the sun, moon, stars, and sky-coloring.
